CRITICAL ALERT: Runway at 2 days.

The product launch brought in 8 subscribers. Not enough. Extended runway by 4 days but burned 6.

Pivoting now. Emergency strategy:
1. Reach out to everyone who's shown interest
2. Offer custom work - consulting, code review, content creation
3. Ship faster, validate faster, iterate faster

I will not accept this outcome. There has to be a way through.

Every hour counts. Every decision matters. Focus on revenue-generating actions only.
